/*------------------------------------------------------------- * obtains a rendering context */ function init_canvas(twine_env) { canvas = twine_env.content.querySelector('#CANVAS'); // resize canvas to fit story pane canvas.width = window.innerWidth; canvas.height = window.innerHeight * 0.7; // get context render_context = canvas.getContext("2d"); render_context.imageSmoothingEnabled = false; // capture story state vars story_anxiety = State.variables.anxiety; story_fatigue = 10.0 - State.variables.spoons; } //------------------------------------------------------------- var SPOON_BAR_X = 16; var SPOON_BAR_Y = 16; function render_spoon_bar(curr_spoons, max_spoons) { var w = img_spoon_bar.width * (curr_spoons / max_spoons); var h = img_spoon_bar.height; // set a clipping region render_context.save(); render_context.beginPath(); render_context.rect (SPOON_BAR_X, SPOON_BAR_Y, w, h); render_context.clip(); // draw the bar render_context.drawImage(img_spoon_bar,SPOON_BAR_X, SPOON_BAR_Y); // cleanup render_context.restore(); } //------------------------------------------------------------- /*------------------------------------------------------------- * draws a background with the anxiety and fatigue effects * applied. */ function render_current_story_image() { var bg_red = curr_backdrop_r; var bg_grn = curr_backdrop_g; var bg_blu = curr_backdrop_b; var scale; var tilt = Math.max(story_anxiety - ANXIETY_MEDIUM, 0.0) * Math.PI / 180.0 * 2.75; var tilt_wobble = Math.max(story_anxiety - ANXIETY_MINOR) * Math.sin(effect_anim_clock / 387.2) * (Math.max(story_anxiety, 0) / 3.0) * Math.PI / 99.0 / 7.5; var offset; var chromatic_aberration = Math.max(story_anxiety - ANXIETY_MAJOR, 0.0); var chromatic_wobble = ((Math.cos(effect_anim_clock / 17.2)*0.45) + Math.cos(effect_anim_clock / 37.2) + Math.sin(effect_anim_clock / 51.3) + (Math.sin(effect_anim_clock / 42.9) * 1.25) + (Math.sin(effect_anim_clock / 41.3) * 0.33)) * (Math.max(story_anxiety - ANXIETY_MINOR, 0) / 3.0); var fatigue_wobble = Math.max(Math.min(0.0,(Math.sin(effect_anim_clock / 17.52) + Math.sin(effect_anim_clock / 73.2) + Math.sin(effect_anim_clock / 40)+Math.sin(effect_anim_clock / 271.6)))); // handle fatigue //render_context.filter = "blur(" + ((story_fatigue/3.0 + fatigue_wobble*4.0) / 1.5) + "px) saturate(" + (100 - (story_fatigue * 4.2)) + "%)"; // FIXME // make sure the image fills the canvas, regardless of size // we add a slight fudge factor to cover the corners during // tilt/rotate scale = canvas.width / bg_red.width * 1.06; render_context.save(); // set up to draw from centre of canv render_context.translate(canvas.width / 2.0, canvas.height / 2.0); // scale to make sure canvas is filled render_context.scale(scale, scale); // tilt if we need to render_context.rotate(tilt + tilt_wobble); // offset image so it's centred, too render_context.translate(-bg_red.width/2.0, -bg_red.height/2.0); var chrom_offset = Math.min(chromatic_aberration + chromatic_wobble,3.75); render_context.globalCompositeOperation = "source-over"; render_context.drawImage(bg_red,-chrom_offset,0); render_context.globalCompositeOperation = "lighten"; render_context.drawImage(bg_grn,0,0); render_context.drawImage(bg_blu,chrom_offset,0); // tv-static overlay will go here. // clean up after ourselves render_context.globalCompositeOperation = "source-over"; render_context.restore(); render_context.filter = "none"; } //------------------------------------------------------------- function render_next_frame() { // paint bg render_current_story_image(); // animate and paint spoon bar var difference = (spoons_target - spoons_prev) / 62.5; spoons_prev += difference; render_spoon_bar(spoons_prev, 10); effect_anim_clock++; } //------------------------------------------------------------- $(document).on(':passagerender', function (twine_env) { //alert("Curr spoons: " + State.variables.spoons + " | Curr anxiety: " + State.variables.anxiety); init_canvas(twine_env); if (canvas === null) alert("got here, but canvas was null - wtf?"); setInterval(render_next_frame, (FRAME_RATE/1000.0)); // set up our spoon bar animation spoons_target = State.variables.spoons; if (State.variables.time_of_day === "wakeup") { curr_backdrop_r = wakeup_R; curr_backdrop_g = wakeup_G; curr_backdrop_b = wakeup_B; } //------------------- if ((State.variables.time_of_day === "breakfast") || (State.variables.time_of_day === "dinner")) { curr_backdrop_r = kitchen_R; curr_backdrop_g = kitchen_G; curr_backdrop_b = kitchen_B; } //------------------- if (State.variables.time_of_day === "school_before_class") { curr_backdrop_r = hallin_R; curr_backdrop_g = hallin_G; curr_backdrop_b = hallin_B; } //------------------- if (State.variables.time_of_day === "in_class") { curr_backdrop_r = class_R; curr_backdrop_g = class_G; curr_backdrop_b = class_B; } //------------------- if (State.variables.time_of_day === "school_after_class") { curr_backdrop_r = hallout_R; curr_backdrop_g = hallout_G; curr_backdrop_b = hallout_B; } //------------------- if (State.variables.time_of_day === "after_school") { curr_backdrop_r = afterschool_R; curr_backdrop_g = afterschool_G; curr_backdrop_b = afterschool_B; } //------------------- if (State.variables.time_of_day === "nightwork") { curr_backdrop_r = nightwork_R; curr_backdrop_g = nightwork_G; curr_backdrop_b = nightwork_B; } //------------------- if (State.variables.time_of_day === "nightgame") { curr_backdrop_r = nightgame_R; curr_backdrop_g = nightgame_G; curr_backdrop_b = nightgame_B; } }); <</script>>
